~~of men) who withdraws (from his whispering in one’s heart after one
~~remembers allâh). [5] 5. "who whispers in the breasts of mankind. 6.
~~"of jinn and men." __________ [1] (v.112:1) see tauhîd in the glossary
~~(appendix). [2] (v.112:3) a) narrated mu‘âdh bin jabal رضي الله عنه:
